article: President Obama finally broke through the onslaught of Republican debates this week to deliver his State of the Union address (complete with hilarious "don't cry over spilled milk" joke). But his moment in the spotlight was short-lived as the media quickly turned their attention back to the battle to the death between Mitt "Self-Deportation" Romney and Newt "Moon Colony" Gingrich.These stories and more fueled the late night shows this week. Below are my favorite late night clips of the week. What were yours?More comedy videos at: GotchaMediaBlog.com
